data.description: ASSUMABLE 2.875% RATE! Welcome to the Coral Model, built by Richmond Homes. The ONLY HOME WITH A PRIVTE POOL AVAILABLE IN THIS NEIGHBORHOOD! This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home is LOADED WITH UPGRADES. Upon entering through your beautiful glass entry door, you are met with gorgeous tile floors throughout the main floor, entering into the kitchen with shaker cabinets, GRANITE countertops, LARGE Island, farmhouse sink and built in pantry. The OPEN FLOOR PLAN on the main floor is an entertainers dream, as the living room and dining room opens up to the EXTENDED COVERED BACK PATIO and FENCED in backyard fully enclosed with vinyl privacy fence. PANORAMIC SCREENS on the back patio give a flawless view overlooking the BRAND NEW SALTWATER POOL AND SPA with sunshelf, travertine and multi colored lights installed in 2023. Don't stop there, head upstairs and wind down in the relaxing loft area which is currently being used a movie room. Master Bedroom has walk in closet with on suite bathroom equipped with a large shower, double vanities and private toilet room. Additionally, upstairs you will find 2 guest bedrooms, 1 full bathroom with cultured marble and separate laundry room to provide ultimate convenience. 2 car garage has overhead storage and a professionally installed mini split A/C system to keep it cool. Preserve at Sunrise offers 3 playgrounds, community pool, community mailboxes and a gazebo with dock! Call today to make an appointment.
